---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const sampleUrl = '/hidden-profit-review/sample/';
---

<Base
  title="You're on the review waitlist"
  description="Your spot on the Hidden Profit Review waitlist is held. Here is what happens next."
  noindex
>
  <div class="container next-page">
    <div class="book-hero panel">
      <p class="book-kicker">You're on the list</p>
      <h1>Your spot is held.</h1>
      <p class="book-sub">
        The review starts with what you just sent me, not with a sales call.
        Here is exactly what happens from here.
      </p>

      <ol class="wait-steps">
        <li>
          <strong>I read your entry personally</strong> within two business days
          &mdash; every one, no filters, no assistant.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>When a slot opens, you get a private booking invite</strong> by
          email. Invites go out in order. No skipping the line.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Until then, your spot holds</strong> with no obligation. If the
          timing stops working for you, one reply takes you off the list.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="wait-while">
        <p class="wait-while-label">While you wait</p>
        <ul class="book-benefits">
          <li>
            <a href={sampleUrl} data-track="waitlist:sample-click">See a complete worked review</a>
            for a $24M general contractor &mdash; exactly what you'll get.
          </li>
          <li>
            Haven't run the <a href="/scorecard/" data-track="cta:scorecard-waitlist">3-minute scorecard</a> yet?
            It gives me a head start on your entry.
          </li>
          <li>
            Browse <a href="/use-cases/" data-track="waitlist:usecases-click">96 use cases</a>
            from businesses like yours to see what a first fix looks like.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .wait-steps {
      counter-reset: step;
      list-style: none;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .wait-steps li {
      counter-increment: step;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-left: 2.4rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .wait-steps li::before {
      content: counter(step);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0.05rem;
      width: 1.7rem;
      height: 1.7rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--color-copper);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: var(--color-copper);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .wait-while {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      margin-top: 1.75rem;
      padding-top: 1.25rem;
    }

    .wait-while-label {
      color: var(--color-copper);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
  </style>
</Base>
